reviews.review_text: Spoonful outro and Throwin>Playin' I usually listen to shows while writing and nothing really perked my ears until (as taper notes state) the Spoonful Garcia outro -- where No one's Fault meets Russian Lullaby... very interesting and unique piece of Jerry improv... The jam between Throwin' Stones and Playin' to end the show also pretty sweet. Thanks to CM and all who made this avail -- nice piece of audio history
